profile_positions.description:
When I was working in the Information and Communication section of IRC, I took care of the following activities:
- Management and development of Francophone and Hispanophone web-, email- and print-based newsletter with partners in Burkina Faso and Colombia;
- Project management of a Customer Relationship Management (CRM) solution: planning, implementation, maintenance, training and follow-up activities; 
- Training sessions on setting up website and managing communication online in partner countries (Burkina Faso, Colombia). 
- Knowledge management activities: E-conference, participation in elaborating KM plans, setting up various Communities of Practice and other internal knowledge-sharing platforms and processes.
- Website content analysis and reorganisation, overall IRC online branding strategy, marketing strategy.
